Network analysis of alternative medicine attitudes

Szilvia Zörgő, Samvel Mkhitaryan & Gjalt-Jorn Peters

February 6, 2019

Analyses

Setup

Loading and preparing data

dat <-
  haven::read_sav(file.path(dataPath,
                            'database.orig.new labels.sav'));

### Set group as factor
dat$group <-
  factor(dat$group,
         levels=1:2,
         labels=c("Alternative medicine",
                  "Medicine"));

### Extract and store attitude variable names
attitudeVars <-
  grep('ATT1_',
       names(dat),
       value=TRUE);
